      "title": "Determination of the blow-up rate for the semilinear wave equation",
      "abstract": "In this paper, we find the optimal blow-up rate for the semilinear wave equation with a power nonlinearity. The exponent p is superlinear and less than 1 + 4 N\u22121 if N \u2265 2."
